{
  "description": "A panoramic view of a city nestled along a coastline, bathed in the warm, golden light of either sunrise or sunset. The city sprawls across a relatively flat area, with a mix of residential and commercial buildings visible. A large body of water \u2013 a bay or estuary \u2013 dominates the midground, reflecting the golden light and creating a shimmering effect. A long bridge extends across the water, connecting different parts of the city or leading to distant land.  In the foreground, lush green vegetation, likely trees, frames the view, adding depth and a natural element. Above, dramatic clouds filter the light, creating beams that highlight specific areas of the city and water. The overall composition suggests a peaceful yet grand urban landscape.",
